<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/EkolimpicChampsGeneralKnowledge.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1620" title="EkolimpicChampsGeneralKnowledge" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/EkolimpicChampsGeneralKnowledge.jpg" alt="" width="248" height="204" /></a></p>
