<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/EkolimpicChampsMahboim.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1624" title="EkolimpicChampsMahboim" src="http://blog.ekoloko.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/EkolimpicChampsMahboim.jpg" alt="" width="297" height="179" /></a></p>
